{"tid":1104915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡劣天氣下廣九直通車多班列車延誤或取消","createTime":"2019-04-13T13:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T13:06:51.000Z","uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3d8730c4a7d9af377b2e25b00ab4889d970239","tid":1104915,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】受惡劣天氣影響，廣九直通車有多班列車延誤或者取消。<br />\n<br />\n兩班來往廣州東站至紅磡站的直通車，分別延遲大約三小時；另外有四班取消，旅客可於30日內辦理退票手續。<br />\n<br />\n在紅磡站，有港鐵職員向旅客講解列車狀況，又貼出告示牌，提醒旅客有列車延誤。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，廣九直通車內地路段因惡劣天氣限速，港鐵呼籲旅客留意網站及紅磡站的最新公布，又對造成旅客不便致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=344403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D344403&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhN5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=7fc9ef02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D344403&h=65e7c0fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=344403</a>"}]}